jobs.title: Marketing Assistant
jobs.description:
* Market Development:
- Develop and implement market development plans, identify and explore potential customers and market opportunities.
- Conduct brand promotion and market development through online channels (e.g., social media, email marketing, SEO/SEM, content marketing).
- Participate in offline activities (e.g., industry exhibitions, seminars, client visits) to expand brand influence.
* Customer Maintenance:
- Establish and maintain relationships with existing customers, conduct regular follow-ups to understand customer needs and provide solutions.
- Handle customer feedback and complaints to ensure customer satisfaction and loyalty.
- Maintain good communication with customers, follow up on orders and project progress to ensure customer requirements are met.
* Market Analysis:
- Collect and analyze market data, research market trends, consumer behavior, and competitor dynamics.
- Develop market research plans, conduct market research, generate analysis reports, and provide improvement suggestions.
- Use data analysis tools to monitor market activity effectiveness and optimize marketing strategies.

Để tiếp tục mở rộng thị trường và nâng cao tầm ảnh hưởng của thương hiệu, chúng tôi chân thành mời những tài năng xuất sắc gia nhập đội ngũ của chúng tôi.
